---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---

<section class="relative bg-jcf-black py-20 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 opacity-10 translate-x-1/4 -translate-y-1/4">
     <svg width="600" height="400" viewBox="0 0 300 200" fill="none">
        <path d="M50 150 L100 50 L150 150" stroke="white" stroke-width="20"/>
        <path d="M120 150 L170 50 L220 150" stroke="#F28E2B" stroke-width="20"/>
     </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
        CONSTRUA COM <span class="text-jcf-orange">CONFIANÇA</span> E QUALIDADE.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-jcf-grey text-lg md:text-xl mb-10 font-medium">
        Tudo o que a sua obra precisa, desde o alicerce ao acabamento. Visite os nossos catálogos ou peça já o seu orçamento.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/catalogos" class="bg-jcf-orange hover:bg-jcf-yellow text-jcf-black px-8 py-4 rounded font-black transition-all flex items-center gap-2">
          VER CATÁLOGOS
        </a>
        <a href="/contactos" class="border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-jcf-black px-8 py-4 rounded font-black transition-all">
          CONTACTAR AGORA
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>